@section The Action Replay
@cindex Action Replay
@cindex Clients, Action Replay

This client records your games and lets you replay them at any speed.
Use the keyboard to control it; when the @dfn{Action Replay} window
is active, press the @kbd{R} key to begin the replay (even if you're
still playing; though it's a good idea to pause the game before doing
